snippet.title: Crab Rhapsody (Vol.1) Trailer
snippet.description: Crabby will never cry, and Rock n’ Roll will never die! Crab Rhapsody (vol.1) (蟹蟹狂想曲) is a FREE musical action-roguelite game with fast-paced combat and original soundtracks.
